cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to an unknown enum 'nia9' will cause security negotiation failures and prevent UE registration.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator server address to a malformed hostname 'server..invalid' will cause DNS resolution failures and prevent RF simulation connections.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器伺服器地址設定為格式錯誤的主機名稱 'server..invalid' 會導致 DNS 解析失敗，並阻止 RF 模擬連接。
